# Processing API - Tests
# Base URL - change according to your environment
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Complete test flow (using variables)

# Step 1: Create processing
# @name createProcess
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/processing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "prod-flow-test",
  "product": "Test Flow Product",
  "price": 999.99
}

### Step 2: Extract processId from response
@flowProcessId = {{createProcess.response.body.$.processId}}

### Step 3: Check status with the generated ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/processing/{{flowProcessId}}/status

### Step 4: Track SSE (keeps connection - run separately)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/processing/{{flowProcessId}}/stream